    <p class="hero-sub">We tested Originality.ai across AI detection accuracy, plagiarism checking, fact-checking, full site scans, and false positive rates. Here's what it catches, where it misses, what it costs, and who actually needs it.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/checkout/" class="btn btn-primary"><span>Try theStacc instead — $1 trial <span class="arrow">→</span></span></a>
