    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS ORIGINALITY.AI -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">What is Originality.ai</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">An <span class="accent">AI content detection platform</span> built for agencies and publishers with editorial standards.</h2>
      <p>Originality.ai launched in 2022 as AI writing tools started flooding content pipelines. Users paste text, upload documents, or scan entire websites to determine whether content was written by humans, AI systems, or a combination. The platform has expanded beyond detection to include plagiarism checking, factual claim verification, readability analysis, and team collaboration with role-based access control.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
