    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Pros</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Where Originality.ai shines</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Five genuine strengths at this price point.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
