              <p>Claims 97%+ accuracy and generally outperforms GPTZero and Copyleaks in head-to-head comparisons on pure AI-generated content. If you're checking unedited AI output, this is the most reliable tool in the category.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>All-in-one content integrity suite</h4>
              <p>AI detection, plagiarism checking, fact-checking, readability analysis, and team management in one platform. Agencies don't need separate tools for each function — that's real operational value at $14.95/month.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
