            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Deep Scan sentence-level explanation</h4>
              <p>Shows exactly which sentences triggered the flag and provides guidance on ethical editing. More useful than a single probability score when working with writers on revision.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Team management with role-based access</h4>
              <p>Admin, Manager, and User roles with tag organization and shareable branded PDF reports. Handles multi-client agency workflows cleanly without jumping between accounts.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
