        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Zero SEO capabilities</h4>
              <p>Detecting AI content does not improve search rankings. Google doesn't penalize AI content — it penalizes low-quality content. Originality.ai has no keyword research, no optimization scoring, and no publishing features.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Accuracy drops sharply on edited AI content</h4>
              <p>Detection rates fall to 60–75% on human-edited AI drafts — the standard workflow for most businesses using AI writing tools. The headline accuracy figures apply only to unedited, raw AI output.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>False positives damage workflows</h4>
