            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Readability analysis</h4>
              <p>Reading grade level, sentence length variation, passive voice usage, grammar and spelling errors. The basic writing quality audit that editors run manually — automated and returned alongside the AI score.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Full site scanning</h4>
              <p>Audit entire domains for AI content in minutes. For publishers managing large content portfolios or due-diligence audits on potential site acquisitions, this alone justifies the subscription.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">06</span>
