    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">Who it's for</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Who should buy Originality.ai — <span class="accent">and who shouldn't.</span></h2>
      <p>The clearest filter we found after testing in real agency and publishing workflows.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col after">
