          <p class="ba-sub">Three signals Originality.ai fits.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>You're a content agency checking freelancer deliverables</h4><p>If you're paying freelancers and need to verify they're not submitting raw AI output, this is the most accurate tool for that job.</p></div></li>
